## 5. Status Lifecycle Diagram

```
                ┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐
                │  DEO creates section draft (storeDraft)    │
                │  → STATUS=SECTION_DRAFT, type=section_draft│
                │  → holder = own dept secretary             │
                └─────────────────┬──────────────────────────┘
                                  │
                                  ▼
   ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │ Secretary opens it (showDraftActions = true)              │
   │ Choices:                                                  │
   │  ① Edit drafted content (updateDraftContent)              │
   │  ② Sign & Forward (forwardToNextDepartment)               │
   │       → unsigned remarks_added converted in-place to      │
   │         signed_and_forwarded                              │
   │       → type=external, current_dept=target,               │
   │         status=PENDING_SECRETARY                          │
   │  ③ Return to Section (returnToSection)                    │
   │       → holder=DEO, status=SECTION_DRAFT                  │
   │       → DEO sees it in My Drafts (returned card)          │
   │  ④ Share Internally (shareInternally)                     │
   │       → status=SHARED_INTERNALLY, internal_forwards rows  │
   └─────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │
                     ▼  (after sign & forward)
   ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │ Receiving Dept Secretary's INBOX                          │
   │ status=PENDING_SECRETARY                                  │
   │ Can:                                                      │
   │  ① Add Remarks & Forward (forwardToNextDepartment)        │
   │  ② Share Internally (shareInternally) → status=SHARED_INT │
   └─────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │ (Share Internally)
                     ▼
   ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │ Internal users see "Pending Action"                       │
   │ Each can:                                                 │
   │  ① Open Action Page → draft remarks + flags + links       │
   │     (submitInternalAction) → creates remarks_added (un-   │
   │     signed) movement, updates internal_forward.status=2   │
   │     → status=READY_TO_FORWARD or SECTION_DRAFT (if origin │
   │       dept) and holder back to secretary                  │
   │  ② Forward to Another User (forwardInternally) → chain   │
   └─────────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                     │ (after remarks submitted)
                     ▼
   ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │ Secretary sees "Drafted Remarks" pending in their tab     │
   │ showDraftActions = true (because hasUnsignedDeptRemarks)  │
   │ Same 4 actions as the section-draft secretary view        │
   │ ──> Sign & Forward will finalize the unsigned remarks_    │
   │     added in place → one signed row on the document       │
   └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

