## 13. Summary Number Generation

```
SUM/{ABBR}/{YEAR}/{6-digit-zero-padded-sequence}

Where:
  ABBR = uppercase initials of each word in the originating department title
         (e.g. "Information Department" → "ID")
  YEAR = current year (4 digits)
  Sequence = next available integer for this dept+year combination

The sequence is generated inside a transaction with lockForUpdate
to prevent collisions.
```

